    %main.single-main
      %section.l-single-container
        %h2.l-single-head.registration 会員情報入力
        %form.l-single-inner.registration-form   
          .l-single-content     
          = form_for @user, url: signup_sms_confirmation_path,  method: :get do |f|
            .form-group
              %label{:for => "nickname"} ニックネーム
              %span.form-require 必須
              = f.text_field :nickname, placeholder: "例）メルカリ太郎", class: "input-default"
            .form-group
              %label{:for => "email"} メールアドレス
              %span.form-require 必須
              = f.email_field :email, placeholder: "PC・携帯どちらでも可", class: "input-default"
            .form-group
              %label{for: "password"} パスワード
              %span.form-require 必須
              = f.password_field :password, placeholder: "7文字以上", class: "input-default"
            .form-group
              %label{for: "password_confirmation"} パスワード (確認)
              %span.form-require 必須
              = f.password_field :password_confirmation, placeholder: "7文字以上", class: "input-default"
            .form-group
              %h3.text-left.l-chapter-sub-head 本人確認
              %p.l-single-text
                安心・安全にご利用いただくために、お客さまの本人情報の登録にご協力ください。他のお客さまに公開されることはありません。
            .form-group
              %div
                %label お名前(全角)
                %span.form-require 必須
                = f.text_field :firstname, placeholder: "例）メルカリ", class: "input-default.half"
                = f.text_field :lastname, placeholder: "例）太郎", class: "input-default.half"
            .form-group
              %div
              %label お名前(カナ)
              %span.form-require 必須
              = f.text_field :firstname_kana, placeholder: "例）メルカリ", class: "input-default.half"
              = f.text_field :lastname_kana, placeholder: "例）タロウ", class: "input-default.half"
